- "top three money makers" refers to the top 3 actors with the highest total worldwide revenue; 
- "silver screen" is a metaphorical term referring to the film industry; 
- "blockbusters" refers to movies with a budget greater than $50 million and released within the last 10 years.

sql:
SELECT budget, domestic_revenue, worldwide_revenue
FROM financials
WHERE movie_id = '0';
